Yang, what's wrong with your arm?

996
00:44:12,159 --> 00:44:13,199
Did you break your arm?

997
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:14,840
Does it hurt?

998
00:44:14,840 --> 00:44:15,719
It's okay.

999
00:44:16,119 --> 00:44:17,280
